## 🚨 MANDATORY RULES (Always enforce)

| Phase | Rule | Consequence |
|-------|------|-------------|
| 1 | If ambiguous → **Ask, don't assume** | Scope creep, regressions |
| 2 | Verify dari **source code**, bukan docs aja | Hallucination, wrong implementation |
| 3 | Define scope **SEBELUM** code phase | Touch unrelated files, break things |
| 4 | Only touch **in-scope files** | Scope creep, side effects |
| 5 | Test MUST PASS, manual smoke required | Silent bugs, regressions |
| 6 | Include test results + files changed | No accountability, undocumented work |

---

## ❌ NEVER (Anti-hallucination Checklist)

- ❌ Langsung code tanpa Fase 1-3
- ❌ Asumsi behavior tanpa verifikasi source code
- ❌ Ubah file di luar scope (dari Fase 3)
- ❌ Skip test verification
- ❌ Report "done" tanpa bukti (test results, files changed)
- ❌ Make up file paths or functions (verify exist first)
- ❌ Change config/env without documenting why
- ❌ Leave TODOs or incomplete work

---

## ⚡ SHORTCUT (Fase 1 + 5 only)

Untuk **trivial tasks** (typo fix, config one-liner, simple UI tweak, docs update):
- **ONLY run:** Fase 1 (understand) + Fase 5 (verify)
- Skip Fase 2-4

**Untuk complex** (Feature, bugfix, API change, schema migration, permission logic):
- **FULL 6-fase WAJIB**

**Decision rule:** "Will this touch >1 file or change behavior?" → Complex task → Full 6-fase.

